name: Winston Carlile
bio: Winston is a senior working towards a degree in Computer Science with a minor in Cognitive Science. After getting hooked on robotics in high school, he now enjoys working on various AI projects in his spare time. His main goal in life is to get a Ph.D in AI and pursue research on creating the Artificial General Intelligence. When he's not programming or watching cat videos, he can be seen working out at the gym, playing raquetball, or eating food.
